<br>
I wonder if there would be support for a change of the number of spell slots.<br>
Now, I don't play EQ for long enough to know if VI ever said something about this or if that was proposed already, but I think it would be nice and reasonable if the number of spells slots would be increased to 10.<br>
<br>
I think the 8 slots have been there from the beginning. Since then every class got many, many new spells. completely new spell lines were introduced and many MOBs require much more work than the MOBs of 1999.<br>
<br>
as it is now you hardly can be prepared well for most battles.<br>
whenever I think I should load another spell I also know that I have to take off a spell I also &quot;urgently&quot; need.<br>
<br>
So what is the opinion of others about that? <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=170427" target="_blank">
<img src="http://www.euphorion.org/sig/euph_zdd2.jpg" border="0">
